              <td width="80" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">非常不喜欢</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="77" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">4</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="67" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">.9</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="92" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">.9</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="97" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">100.0</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
             </tr> 
             <tr> 
              <td width="80" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">Total</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="77" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">460</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="67" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">99.8</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="92" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">100.0</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="97" valign="center" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;"> <span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;">&nbsp;</span> </p> </td> 
             </tr> 
             <tr> 
              <td width="63" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">Missing</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="80" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">System</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="77" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">1</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="67" valign="top" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">.2</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="92" valign="center" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;"> <span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;">&nbsp;</span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="97" valign="center" style="border:1.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;"> <span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;">&nbsp;</span> </p> </td> 
             </tr> 
             <tr> 
              <td width="143" valign="top" colspan="2" style="border:2.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">Total</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="77" valign="top" style="border:2.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">461</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="67" valign="top" style="border:2.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:3.0000pt;text-align:right;"> <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;">100.0</span><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9.0000pt;"></span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="92" valign="center" style="border:2.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;"> <span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;">&nbsp;</span> </p> </td> 
              <td width="97" valign="center" style="border:2.0000pt solid #000000;background:#FFFFFF;"> <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;"> <span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;">&nbsp;</span> </p> </td> 
             </tr> 
            </tbody> 
           </table> <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21pt;"> 从以上的表格中，我们看到，选择非常喜欢、喜欢国产动画片的人数有263人，加起来占总数的57.9%，而对外国动画片的喜爱程度，选择喜欢和非常喜欢的人数加起来达到236人，占总数的51.2%。这表明，儿童对国产动画片的喜爱程度略高于外国动画片。 </p> <p class="MsoNormal"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在深度访谈的调查中，当问及“你最喜欢看什么动画片”时，《熊出没》和《喜羊羊与灰太狼》两部国产动画片的选择率很高，分别有14人和11人选择。排名第三的则是美国的经典动画片《猫和老鼠》，5人选择。这也证明了，近几年来，国产动画片发展势头良好，在中国青少年儿童心目中的地位已经赶超了外国动画片。 </p> <p class="MsoNormal"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（五）国产动画片存在的问题 </p> <p class="MsoNormal"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不可否认，近几年来我国的动画片有了较大的将发展，形势大好。但是，并不意味着我国的动漫产业就已经达到“强国”的位置。应该看到，我们与美日等动漫大国之前还存在较大的差距。为进一步探讨国产动画片存在的问题，我们设置了8个选项供家长选择，分别是画面美感差、类型单一、&nbsp;故事情节俗套没创意、人物设置呆板，基本以动物为主、音效效果差、内容幼稚教育意义不大、分年龄分等级的动画片少内容成人化&nbsp;、其他（请注明）。具体频数分析如下： </p> 
           <table class="MsoNormalTable" style="width:366.9pt;"> 
            <tbody> 
             <tr> 
